\newlabel{fig:parameter_heatmap}{{1}{6}{\small Parameter heatmap comparing MV and UV forecasting accuracy across window lengths and horizons (based on MAPE). The upper plot is for Rates and the lower one is for Stocks. In each plot, the left side is for the 21 working day forecast (1 month forecast) and the right side is for the 63 working day forecast (3 month forecast)}{figure.1}{}}
